<h3 class="lt-blue">Highlights In Your State</h3>
<p>Unfortunately, there hasn't been a lot of recent MJFF activity in your area. Be the first to host an event! Check out <a href="https://www.michaeljfox.org/get-involved/be-a-fundraiser.html" style="color: orange;">this list</a> of events to kickstart your own ideas. <a href="https://www.michaeljfox.org/foundation/news-detail.php?Norman-Oklahomas-First-Team-Fox-Gala" style="color: orange;">Nicole's story</a> shows how valuable it is to become the first MJFF event host in your area.</p>
<div style="margin-bottom: 10px; margin-top: 10px;"><a href="https://www.michaeljfox.org/get-involved/be-a-fundraiser.html" class="mjffButton">Start Your Own Event</a></div>
<p style="margin-top: 20px;" class="h-divider"> </p>
<h3 class="lt-blue">Global Online Events</h3>
<p>The Michael J. Fox Foundation offers high-quality educational programs to inform you about research progress in Parkinson’s disease. Join our <a href="/page.html?hot-topics-webinar-series" style="color: orange;">Hot Topics Webinars</a> to learn more about our urgent pursuit of medical breakthroughs, and submit your own questions for our expert panel.</p>
<p>Webinars cover different topics of interest to Parkinson’s patients and their loved ones. They are moderated by Dave Iverson, a Parkinson’s patient, veteran journalist and contributing editor to The Michael J. Fox Foundation. Archived recordings of the Webinars offer on-demand access following the original live event.</p>
<p>All Michael J. Fox Foundation educational initiatives are offered free of charge. We hope you’ll join us soon.</p>
<div style="padding-bottom: 10px;"><a href="/page.html?hot-topics-webinar-series" style="display: inline; color: orange; font-size: 1.4em;" class="learnMoreLink">Learn More</a></div>
<p class="h-divider"> </p>
<h3 class="lt-blue">Contact</h3>
<p>Want to get in touch? Foundation staff members regularly engage with the broader Parkinson’s community in your area through speaking engagements and events. Contact our <a href="mailto:hoppenheimer@michaeljfox.org" style="color: orange;">Development staff</a> or <a href="mailto:hoppenheimer@michaeljfox.org" style="color: orange;">Team Fox</a>.</p>
